data.description:
Tucked away just minutes from I-75, Broder Farm in Stockbridge offers 4 sides brick new townhomes in a resort-style oasis with convenient access to shopping, dining and entertainment. Featuring a community pool with cabana, playground, dog park, athletic field and walking trails, every day will be a stay-cation. 
 Low maintenance and spacious, this incredible three-bedroom townhome design is built for today's lifestyles. And you will never be too far from home with Home Is Connected.® Your new home is built with an industry leading suite of smart home products that keep you connected with the people and place you value most. The island kitchen allows for bar stool seating and opens to the family room and a casual dining area. Upstairs offers a private bedroom suite with spa-like bath plus gracious secondary bedrooms with lots of closet space and laundry. Photos used for illustrative purposes and do not depict actual home.
